data.enText: a person, usually a man, whose job is to put out fires

tr: play in which children pretend to put out a fire
a member of a fire department who tries to extinguish fires
a pitcher who does not start the game
a laborer who tends fires (as on a coal-fired train or steamship)

value.def: A fireman is a person, usually a man, whose job is to put out fires.
value.tran: (通常指男性)消防队员，救火队员

trans: 救火员；消防员；消防队员；火男；消防人员
